♂ (SCAU WL30), China, Guangxi Zhuang Autonomous Region, Hechi City, 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Du’an">Du'an</normalizedToken>
Yao Autonomous County, Napang Dong, 
<geoCoordinate degrees="24" direction="north" minutes="08" orientation="latitude" precision="15" seconds="22" value="24.139444">24°08'22&quot;N</geoCoordinate>
, 
<geoCoordinate degrees="107" direction="east" minutes="51" orientation="longitude" precision="15" seconds="07" value="107.851944">107°51'07&quot;E</geoCoordinate>
, 650 m alt., 2015-VII-26, leg. Chen Jujian, Wang Xinhui &amp; Tang Mingruo. 
<emphasis bold="true" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="89">Paratypes</emphasis>
: 2 ♂, 12 ♀ (SCAU WL30), same data as the holotype. 3 ♂, 4 ♀ (SCAU G72), same County, Cave Bianfu Dong, 
<geoCoordinate degrees="24" direction="north" minutes="01" orientation="latitude" precision="15" seconds="55" value="24.031944">24°01'55&quot;N</geoCoordinate>
, 
<geoCoordinate degrees="108" direction="east" minutes="20" orientation="longitude" precision="15" seconds="12" value="108.33667">108°20'12&quot;E</geoCoordinate>
